title: Alexa & Carlos PenaVega Are Stars Wars Super Fans At DWTS Studio
text: Alexa & Carlos PenaVega Are Stars Wars Super Fans At DWTS Studio Monday, 26 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) Alexa PenaVega and her husband Carlos pose with Yoda outside the dance studio on Friday afternoon (October 23). The couple got a couple shots with the figure and a lightsaber before heading home after practice with their pro partners, Witney Carson and Mark Ballas. PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Witney Carson “This weeks [...] Today Your source for all things celebrity and entertainment. Carlos PenaVega has two women in his life right now—his wife (and Dancing With the Stars competitor) Alexa PenaVega , and his DWTS pro partner, Witney Carson .
